data.description: Prime Location in the Heart of Maspeth! 1 Family Detached Brick Colonial on a 20 x 100  lot. This home offers 3 generous bedrooms, 1 full bath and 1 half bath. Spacious rooms throughout, formal dining room and living room, eat-in kitchen (with access to your large enclosed private yard), hardwood floors, high ceilings and plenty of storage space. Great Location & Great Opportunity! Close to all!  Conveniently located off Grand Avenue near LIE, BQE, Queens Blvd. Schools, Shops, Restaurants, Buses, and Subway (R&M)  A MUST SEE!
